<h2 class="bold font-l">Belt of Grenades</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Henry throws the grenade at the guards but it comes back to him before he can close the door. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="p5cjle" data-video-descrip="Agent Washington makes the mistake of asking Caboose to throw a grenade to help Church. Fortunately, it doesn't hit Church like it usually would. Unfortunately for Wash..." data-video-title="Worst Throw Ever. Of All Time." data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/p5cjle_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/p5cjle.jpg" data-video-trope="Main/ExplosiveStupidity" data-video-tropename="Explosive Stupidity" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="Machinima/RedVsBlue,Machinima/RedVsBlueTheRecollection" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/p5cjle.jpg">
